SELECT [Purchase Line].[Document No_], [Purchase Line].[Model Item No_], Item.[Description 2], [Purchase Line].[Variable Code 01] AS [Col Code], [Variable Code].Description AS [Col Description], [Purchase Line].[Variable Code 02] AS [Size], [FW24 CPH_Linesheet-size-ean].copenhagen_id, Val([purchase line.quantity]) AS qty_pairs, [Purchase Line_1].[Assortment Code], IIf([Purchase Line_1.type]=20,Val([purchase line_1.quantity]),"") AS qty_ass, [Purchase Line].[requested receipt date] AS [requested delivery date]
FROM (((([Purchase Header] INNER JOIN ([Purchase Line] INNER JOIN [NavisionEan-step0] ON [Purchase Line].No_ = [NavisionEan-step0].[Item No_]) ON ([Purchase Header].No_ = [Purchase Line].[Document No_]) AND ([Purchase Header].[Document Type] = [Purchase Line].[Document Type])) INNER JOIN Item ON [Purchase Line].[Model Item No_] = Item.No_) INNER JOIN [Variable Code] ON ([Purchase Line].[Variable Code 01] = [Variable Code].[Variable Code]) AND ([Purchase Line].[Variable Group 01] = [Variable Code].[Variable Group])) INNER JOIN [FW24 CPH_Linesheet-size-ean] ON [NavisionEan-step0].[Cross-Reference No_] = [FW24 CPH_Linesheet-size-ean].ean) INNER JOIN [Purchase Line] AS [Purchase Line_1] ON ([Purchase Line].[Document No_] = [Purchase Line_1].[Document No_]) AND ([Purchase Line].[Original Line No_] = [Purchase Line_1].[Line No_])
WHERE ((([Purchase Line].[Document No_])=[forms]![principale]![FiltroODAEstrazioneTemplateNapa]) AND (([Purchase Line].Type)=2));

